My go-to slick back bun ft. @sexyhair products 🤍

Steps: 
1. Use about 2-4 pumps of blow dry volumizing gel and run through your roots and mid length 
2. Gather all your hair with a regular hairbrush and secure tightly into a pony tail then use a boar wood brush to brush back hair any baby hairs
3. Twist your pony tail and wrap it around tightly as possible and secure with another hair tie 
4. Lastly, grab an eyebrow brush and spray hairspray on it and brush front to back for a super clean look!
